CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

February 15, 2011

[Cite as 02/15/2011 Case Announcements, 2011-Ohio-672.]

*1543MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2010-0180. In re C.B.

Cuyahoga App. No. 92775. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County.

Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to vary time for oral argument, it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
